component_text: I remember walking threw the library in town and seeing a large quantity of books
None of these books really seemed offensive
this library had an upstairs that the more 'colorful' books were at
They should not be banned though, they should only be moved
i remember walking threw the library trying to find a book to help me with an assignment at skool and i seen several young kids looking at some adult books and magazines
these were put here for advertisements,
they should be advertised in different areas out of site of kids and teenagers
it would be nice to see some books and magazines banned,
anything should ever be banned for what it says or shows or sounds like
instead of showing certain things at low levels where younger people can get there hands on, they should be at a higher level or behind the desk
